--------------------------------------------------------------
CTB_G4Sim: Geant4 ATLAS simulation of the CTB 2004 
             Atlas Combined Test Beam   
--------------------------------------------------------------

  This is a pseudo-package that contains the jobOptions in use 
for the CTB 2004 simulation. The CTB simulation is using since 
ATLAS 10.0.1 release the Python infrastructure for simulation 
hosted by G4AtlasApps package. 

  The "old" Geant4 macro file simulation description is kept 
under CTB_G4Sim/G4macros/ and it is NOT SUPPORTED and OBSOLETE. 

M. Gallas 

NEWS: 
     in ATLAS releases >= 13.0.10 the simulation of the muon 
   system is not supported. 

