---------
Examples:
---------
(under CTB_G4Sim/share)

jobOptions.G4Ctb_SimProd.py        ---> typical jobOption 
                                       for simulation
jobOptions.G4Ctb_SimProd_photon.py  ---> jobOption for the 
                                        "selected" photon runs   
jobOptions.G4Ctb_DigProd.py         ---> jobOption for 
                                       digitization  
jobOptions.G4Ctb_SimExamples.py     ---> examples for 
                                       simulation  

--------------------
Run conditions data:
--------------------
(under CTB_G4Sim/share)

+ CtbRunConditionsData.py             
run conditions for the _Combined CTB period_. This means in terms of
real data:
   from 2101725  to 2102986 and this range covers also the 
   photon period that starts at 2102775
In this file the 4 last digits are enough to identify the run

+ CaloRunConditionsData.py
run conditions for the calo data period. 

(under CTB_G4Sim/python)
 
+ CtbPhotonESpectrum.py 
photon energy spectrum for the CTB photon runs. Not all the runs are 
included.  
  
